Package com.microsoft.azure.management.keyvault

Interface Key

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasId, HasInner<KeyBundle>, HasName, Indexable, Updatable<Key.Update>

    @Beta(V1_6_0)
public interface Key
extends Indexable, HasInner<KeyBundle>, HasId, HasName, Updatable<Key.Update>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure Key Vault key.
